Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.16,0:00:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我爸媽去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天中午之前都不會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.71,0:00:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天要一個人看家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要自己做晚飯啊 好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.28,0:00:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得好冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要一條圍巾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今晚順便去看看唄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕的話就直說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.81,0:00:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要去小綾家住宿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲收拾好了嗎 要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些用不著的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶國語詞典也沒什麼用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家的聖書被說成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去可憐家 然後一起去小綾家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住址好像就是這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那所公寓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.33,0:01:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 是幾號房間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有都是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整棟都是可憐家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨 一直在等你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.28,0:01:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.00,0:01:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外頭很冷吧 快進屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手 好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你一直在外面等著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見你們遲遲沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.43,0:01:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有些擔心你們…才沒有擔心你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:35.40,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\bord1\fad(400,400)\be3\3c&H5680A5&\pos(686.063,442.998)\c&HFFFFFF&}是誰還沒睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 去了趟便利店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是剛到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綾的房間好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐 那裡不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有私房錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是放內衣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:03:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人的第六感…感覺應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透視嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去做晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐也要來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 馬鈴薯燉牛肉怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像忘了點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調味料怎麼加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把醬油倒進大勺子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 倒入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹估量一下倒入的量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂啦 反正都是目測
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然陽子的優點是大方灑脫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缺點就是粗枝大葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是在誇我還是在損我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們把雞蛋打在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ok~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 之前看過有人用頭打雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也看過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲 可憐 雞蛋打好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用頭敲的又不是生雞蛋是煮熟的雞蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡水已經準備好了 你們兩個先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要泡泡機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡泡什麼？抱歉 沒有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有入浴劑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是花香之類的 想要哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要木貫的浴缸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個可能…不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:06:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金髮少女們洗澡的氛圍 相當有藝術感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs25\pos(368.35,384)}生\N發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.29,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有護髮素 是阿綾綾的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借用一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立馬變順滑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這是生髮劑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分 你故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 因為是漢字 所以我沒看懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合口味就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗茶淡飯 不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才不是說好像忘了什麼重要的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為晚餐的配菜 媽媽給我們做了土豆燉肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請品嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機真不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥兒 謝謝你們今天留宿在這裡陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了大家 我好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一個人的話 我想我晚上會睡不著的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都喜歡可怕的鬼故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…果然還是要加入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們的鬼故事大會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.25,0:07:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早飯我都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 很好吃的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 雞蛋卷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.29,0:07:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮睡翹起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「做什麼」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡覺後頭髮很亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.96,0:08:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 您會說繞口令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生麥 生活垃圾 生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然對已經適應了英語的人來說很困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師是外國人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生麥 生活垃圾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 請教教我這裡的發音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師還想請你教教我說繞口令的技巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生麥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小路同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的校服真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然水手服什麼的還是很少見的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說蘭服 像黑貓一樣 真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\pos(325,435)}Gakuran
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭服可是男生的校服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21\pos(305,435)}Gakuran
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不管是男是女穿起來都很不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由和時尚最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全穿走樣了就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像是旅行一樣 真開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我回想起小忍來我家的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}下次來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.98,0:09:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}好想去可憐家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}給你們一人一間房哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿綾綾 有什麼煩心事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是個好天氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐總是精力充沛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率真自由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 Freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 想到了個不錯的點子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐 不 該叫師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收我為徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從第一次見到你時我就很崇拜你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才能變成像你一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我就是阿綾綾的師傅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多賜教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大庭廣眾下 你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得從外表入手比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上這個 我也成不了可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 首先模仿我的說話方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指洋氣的隻言片語說話方式？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 要更流暢點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這樣對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是咿呀學語式的 還怎麼流暢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真你就輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回就在課堂上實戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:10:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小路同學你來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老外口音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綾 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅 我感覺哪裡有點不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 感覺很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是在逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿嘞？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿綾綾 我來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐 請溫柔點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.33,0:11:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 今天我是阿綾綾的師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我大姐頭可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該叫師傅嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:12:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子 你今天不和小綾組隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺今天她好像一直在躲著我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的錯覺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那來和我們一起訓練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓陣多人傳球？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蹴鞠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用腳踢得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒 我從頭給你們教起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做自己不習慣的事真累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我們就去弓道社玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個射擊靶心的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前幾天剛玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐很擅長運動類競技呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連規則都不知道卻能做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.21,0:12:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我根本學不會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐肯定是超級天才
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成不了可憐那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿綾綾為什麼想要成為我這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很嚮往阿綾綾的那種古典風呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是平常的阿綾綾最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.63,0:13:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿綾綾？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綾？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和陽子吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是我對她說了過火的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是不坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說一些惹人討厭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是傲嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話 我就去和她和好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿綾綾 這是今天最後的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 阿綾綾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:13:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綾？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我有話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想買筆記本 能陪我去文具店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要不要也買個新本子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做得太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 就為那事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我一點都沒在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.84,0:14:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 我還以為是招你討厭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.60,0:14:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為了表示和好 我們買一樣的本子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種的如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明不喜歡花飾的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是可憐的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 陽子 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝 謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說今天小綾一直在模仿可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生硬的語調真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿綾綾還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我完美模仿阿綾綾給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小路綾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習方面的事隨便放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一般的可憐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.67,0:16:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 昨天把茶撒到上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你憑什麼說我笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小綾 你這樣就和昨天一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有失弟子資格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩hide-and-seek吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,hide？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 捉迷藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到日本之後一直想玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.33,0:18:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,範圍是整個學校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀 石頭 布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我數30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:19:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}1 2 3 4 5 … 25 30
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:03.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定想不到我沒有離開開始地點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你們見識一下捉迷藏大師可憐真正的實力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了 找到可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個學校的話…可以藏的地方有很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 小學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我沒被人找到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,察覺到的時候 大家全都回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有壞孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐 鬼不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.21,0:19:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 在圖書室裡請安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道已經被找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 那麼去其他地方找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 怎麼可以 再認真找一找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快要走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己反倒跑出來了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打…打擾到你們還真是抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.37,0:20:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是艾莉絲和小忍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道和小忍躲在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好睏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\an8\1c&H123CBF&\bord0\shad0\fr3\pos(531.625,207.334)}小\N忍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲暫且不提 忍可是很難對付的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.64,0:20:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.20,0:20:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去我們經常玩捉迷藏 忍竟然可以隱藏氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\an8}忍 忍 忍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到她毫無聲息藏起來的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.35,0:20:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至懷疑過她的前世是不是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼…鄭重其事地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻手帕好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在英國買的 是我的心愛之物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐 能讓我摸一下那隻手帕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪裡冒出來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉上長出了羽毛…誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美術室的門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲同學 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…死亡訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在動搖 怎麼可以不相信學生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是睡著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 老師太輕率了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為道歉 老師也一起藏起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 沒法告訴她實際上想被快點找到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.49,0:22:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還沒有找過
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲小小的 很難找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲同學 忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.36,0:22:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏丸老師 你做什麼呢 在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 呃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.92,0:22:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說幫忙玩捉迷藏了 我卻先被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.00,0:22:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有多笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.35,0:22:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃 逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲你一個人快點逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師為什麼說出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 竟然在躲藏的時候睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.57,0:22:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因 因為
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真的很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾玩一次也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都這麼開心 我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:23:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 下次玩鬼捉人吧 我來捉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.90,0:23:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在天黑前回家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.14,0:23:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見…是這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.66,0:23:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉絲 鬼捉人用英語怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 叫做tag
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到恐怖故事後就睡不著了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱著玩偶睡覺怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有其他可以代替的東西呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.24,0:23:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱緊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再見
